```
# Rust/Cargo specific ignores
target/
Cargo.lock
**/*.rs.bk

# Dependencies
**/node_modules/
**/.venv/
**/venv/

# Build artifacts
**/build/
**/dist/
**/*.o
**/*.obj
**/*.a
**/*.lib
**/*.dll
**/*.so
**/*.dylib

# Logs and temporary files
**/*.log
**/*.tmp
**/*.swp
**/*.swo

# IDE/Editor files
**/.vscode/
**/.idea/
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
**/*.pyo

# System files
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db

# Environment files
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/*.env.*

# Coverage reports
**/coverage/
**/htmlcov/
**/.coverage

# Test/cache directories
**/.pytest_cache/
**/.mypy_cache/
**/.ruff_cache/
```